标题: 自带效果的武器            大家好这是本人第一次做贴{:10_492:}           我来给大家一个ooc
           也没什么好说就是拿个武器就会有跳跃效果{:10_521:}
           （这个应该没人做过吧）
          下面就是我滴ooc咯
/summon FallingSand ~ ~1 ~ 
{Time:1,Block:"minecraft:redstone_block",Passengers:[{id:"FallingSand",Time:1,Block:"minecraft:activator_rail",Passengers:[{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/fill ~-2 ~ ~-2 ~-7 ~3 ~2 minecraft:air
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/fill ~-2 ~ ~-2 ~-7 ~ ~2 minecraft:bedrock
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/fill ~-2 ~3 ~-2 ~-7 ~3 ~2 minecraft:bedrock
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/fill ~-2 ~1 ~-2 ~-7 ~2 ~2 minecraft:stained_glass 3
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/fill ~-3 ~1 ~-1 ~-6 ~2 ~1 minecraft:air
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~-3 ~1 ~1 minecraft:repeating_command_block 4 replace {conditionMet:1b,auto:1b,Command:"scoreboard players add @a effect 1 {SelectedItem:{id:\\"minecraft:diamond_axe\\",Count:1b,tag:{AttributeModifiers:[{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,Amount:10.0,AttributeName:generic.attackDamage,Name:Attack},{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,Amount:1.0,AttributeName:generic.attackSpeed,Name:Attack},{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,Amount:0.1,AttributeName:generic.movementspeed,Name:Attack}],HideFlags:63,Unbreakable:1,display:{Name:\\"斧头\\",Lore:[\\"神秘的武器\\",\\"（拿上他就会有效果）\\"]}}}}"}
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~-4 ~1 ~1 chain_command_block 4 replace {auto:1b,conditionMet:1b,Command:"/effect @a[score_effect_min=1] 8 1 3 true"}
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~-5 ~1 ~1 chain_command_block 5 replace {auto:1b,conditionMet:1b,Command:"/scoreboard players set @a[score_effect_min=1] effect 0"}
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~-6 ~1 ~1 minecraft:command_block 4 replace {Command:"/give @p minecraft:diamond_axe 1 0 {AttributeModifiers:[{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,Amount:10.0,AttributeName:generic.attackDamage,Name:Attack},{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,Amount:1.0,AttributeName:generic.attackSpeed,Name:Attack},{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,Amount:0.1,AttributeName:generic.movementspeed,Name:Attack}],HideFlags:63,Unbreakable:1,display:{Name:\\"斧头\\",Lore:[\\"神秘的武器\\",\\"（拿上他就会有效果）\\"]}}"}
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~-6 ~1 ~-1 minecraft:command_block 4 replace {Command:"/setblock ~ ~ ~1 minecraft:air"}
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~-1 ~2 ~ wall_sign 5 replace {Text1:"{\\"text\\":\\"信息\\",\\"bold\\":\\"true\\",\\"color\\":\\"white\\",\\"clickEvent\\":{\\"action\\":\\"run_command\\",\\"value\\":\\"setblock ~-5 ~-1 ~ redstone_block\\"}}",Text2:"{\\"text\\":\\"By 小东\\",\\"underlined\\":\\"true\\"}",Text3:"{\\"text\\":\\"只做了一半而且武器没彩色字体\\",\\"italic\\":\\"true\\",\\"strikethrough\\":\\"true\\",\\"color\\":\\"red\\"}",Text4:"{\\"text\\":\\"[右键我获取武器]\\"}"}
"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/scoreboard objectives add effect dummy effect"},{id:"MinecartCommandBlock",Command:"/setblock ~ ~-1 ~ minecraft:lava 15 replace"}]}]}复制代码     我知道很短{:10_516:}请你们不要吐槽！！！
                          
